scene.message:
Mark: Uh...{wait_fr:88}Bleeaargh!{nl}
I'm gonna hurl...{nl}
{ctl0f:1}, you're tougher{nl}
than you look...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Khh, cough...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Likely from forcing{nl}
the transfer.{nl}
Lucky we arrived intact.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Tch...{wait_fr:60}{nl}
What's wrong, Inaba...{nl}
Pathetic.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: ...Tch!{nl}
Look in a mirror, Reiji.{nl}
You're pale as a sheet.{nl}
What are you, a zombie?{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Hmph...{nl}
If you can crack jokes,{nl}
you're fine...{nl}
No time to dawdle.{waitkey}{ret}

Dr. Nicolai: Uugh...{wait_fr:60}{nl}
The hammer of judgment{nl}
upon foolish mankind!{waitkey}Mankind needs no future!{waitkey}{ret}

Dr. Nicolai: Destruction!{nl}
Annihilation!{nl}
Ruin, ruin, ruiiiin!!{waitkey}The hammer upon mankind!{nl}
The song of ruiiiin!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: What's gotten into you?!{nl}
Talking like Kandori...{nl}
Old man!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: That man is now{nl}
but an extension of me.{nl}
{wait_fr:104}No...{waitkey}{clearbox}Even now, people the{nl}
world over wish, like me,{nl}
for mankind's destruction.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Why you...{nl}
What's that supposed{nl}
to mean?!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: You... with that{nl}
mirror, you've brainwashed{nl}
the whole world?!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: All of mankind{nl}
acting under one unified{nl}
will... isn't it splendid?{waitkey}{clearbox}I've achieved a feat{nl}
no ruler ever could...{nl}
I have surpassed humanity.{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: One more word from{nl}
me - a command to kill{nl}
each other - and it is done...{waitkey}{clearbox}A fitting end for fools.{nl}
Nothing else is harmed...{nl}
Only humans vanish{nl}
from this world.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Why?!{nl}
Why do you want{nl}
to erase people?!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: Hmhm...{nl}
Strange words coming{nl}
from you...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Sonomura{wait_fr:60} Maki.{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: The mirror's power{nl}
reaches all. You are{nl}
no exception.{waitkey}Can you reach me?{nl}
Hmhm...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Quit spacing out!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hurry up or Ayase's{nl}
future is gonna disappear!{nl}
Get after him already!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Ngh...{wait_fr:60}{nl}
Thanks, Maki.{nl}
I'm all right now.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Together now, Uesugi.{nl}
You're the leader, right?{nl}
Get a grip.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: I-I know that!{nl}
I was just playing along!{nl}
I'm fine, just watch!{waitkey}Nnngh!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: How's that!{nl}
The leader's the leadah!{nl}
Say it! ...or somethin'.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Right? Right?{nl}
A handsome guy with looks{nl}
AND a funny bone - top class!{waitkey}{clearbox}My rival's Nakai of ZMAP!{nl}
Some knit-cap guy? No contest,{nl}
no contest!{waitkey}Maki, you get it!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Well, even a fool{nl}
has his uses,{nl}
as they say.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: That bastard...{nl}
plotting something{nl}
insane!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...{wait_fr:60}I see.{nl}
So that's it...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Good God...{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...{wait_fr:60}Knowing him,{nl}
no telling what filthy{nl}
tricks he's got ready...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Stay sharp.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Kandori's last words{nl}
bother me...{nl}
And my head aches...{waitkey}{clearbox}{ctl07:1}...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
don't do anything reckless,{wait_fr:60}{nl}
all right?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Damn Kandori!{nl}
We won't let him{nl}
brainwash anyone!{waitkey}...or somethin'.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: {ctl08:65281}This is where you{nl}
laugh, y'know? Laugh, laugh!{nl}
Daaa-hahhahhahha...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: What...{nl}
I'm not putting on{nl}
a brave face or anything!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, {ctl0f:1}~{nl}
Doesn't your head{nl}
kinda hurt?{waitkey}{ret}

Dr. Nicolai: The time of{nl}
final judgment! Why was{nl}
mankind ever born?{waitkey}We who cannot answer{nl}
deserve to perish!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Damn it!{nl}
She's not here!{nl}
Where'd you go, Sonomura?!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: .........{wait_fr:88}{nl}
To think such a system{nl}
opens a path into{nl}
the human heart...{waitkey}{clearbox}So long as this exists,{nl}
no good will come.{nl}
We must destroy it,{nl}
whatever it takes.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...That Sonomura girl.{nl}
If we don't hurry,{nl}
it'll be too late, the{nl}
way she looked.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Shit!{nl}
She's not here!{nl}
We must find her fast!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Argh, not here either!{nl}
Where'd you run off to,{nl}
Maki?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Wrong place!{nl}
She's not here!{nl}
Geez, why'd we even{nl}
come here?{waitkey}{ret}

Dr. Nicolai: Uugh...{nl}
what on earth was I...?{waitkey}{clearbox}What?! Could such a thing be?{nl}
I see... it seems I've{nl}
wronged you all terribly.{waitkey}{clearbox}I beg you as well...{nl}
Please, save Sonomura's{nl}
daughter, whatever it takes!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll adjust the system{nl}
and give my all to reach{nl}
Sonomura at any moment!{waitkey}{nl}
After that...{nl}
I'll accept any judgment.{nl}
I beg you, young man!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: {ctl07:1}!{nl}
Where are you going?!{nl}
We have to beat Kandori, fast!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Where do you think{nl}
you're going?!{waitkey}Aren't we saving Sonomura?!{waitkey}{ret}
